Battle Mage					TYPE:General		SOURCEPAGE:p.55	DESC:Gain spells you can only use if you've been in combat.							PRESTAT:1,STR=13	PRECLASS:1,SPELLCASTER=5										BENEFIT:You may select 6 battle mage spells to become part of your spell list. If you have limited spells known, you do not automatically know these spells, but you may learn three of them for only one spell slot towards your maximum spells known. Each time you successfully hit a foe with a weapon attack not augmented by a spell, you gain one battle mark. Any time you fail an attack roll, you lose one battle mark. You may spend a battle mark to cast one of your known selected spells by spending a spell slot of the same level or higher. Each day when you regain uses of your spells, you lose any unused battle marks.											MULT:YES	CHOOSE:NOCHOICE	BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Battle Mage Spell|6
Blood Magic					TYPE:General		SOURCEPAGE:p.56	DESC:Learn spells you can only cast after taking damage.							PRECLASS:1,SPELLCASTER=5													BENEFIT:You may select 6 blood mage spells to become part of your spell list. If you have limited spells known, you do not automatically know these spells, but you may learn three of them for only one spell slot towards your maximum spells known. Each time you take %1+ hp damage from a single blow or source, or have a -2 or greater penalty inflicted on you as a pain effect, you gain one blood mark. Any time you regain hit points through any method, you lose one blood mark. You may spend a blood mark to cast one of your known selected spells by spending a spell slot of the same level or higher. Each day when you regain uses of your spells, you lose any unused blood marks.|TL	MULT:YES	CHOOSE:NOCHOICE	BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Blood Mage Spell|6

